flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "39DCF299498B1BA56125B5AB4AEA9E44", "The goblins around Foul Grog Lake look angry, scrappy, and hungry. Compared with the sickly variety near Lionhold, these goblins are more resourceful and more menacing. They cause trouble for the Kaelar settlers traveling between Briarmoor and its neighboring farmholds. Try as they might, the Kaelar patrols have trouble keeping the roads safe from their constant mischief. At the lakeside, it appears that a scuffle has taken place between a guard and a goblin ambush. In an endeavor to recover their footing, Kaelar allies rally at the Thornmarch Guard Tower.")
calloutDescription: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "815F36C2483AF09644DB54871C886B6B", "A tower guard with a brightly gleaming broadsword stands at attention. He glances over with a worried expression on his face.")
name: CSQ_0023_FoulPresence
